{"title":"Ecografía en el Shock Indiferenciado","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica/Ecografía en el Shock Indiferenciado-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"","guid":"MtmP6ewZMRwIt2trrCGM8A","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Perlas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"¿Cuál es la definición de shock\\Nséptico según Sepsis-3?","guid":"gI_NeMB-v2uPWM_yJMYYIg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"R: Sepsis con hipotensión persistente que requiere vasopresores para mantener PAM ≥65\\NmmHg e hiperlactatemia >2 mmol/L a pesar de reanimación con volumen adecuado.(21)","guid":"JpGXnbw3YwBfyRPVA5bSIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"¿Cuáles son las metas hemodinámicas\\Niniciales en el manejo del shock séptico?","guid":"CXyuQbBRAL-XaSp9tojhoQ","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"R: PAM >65 mmHg, FC <120 lpm, SatO2 >94%, Hb >7-8 g/dL, uso de norepinefrina\\Ncomo primer vasopresor y cristaloides como fluido de elección.(2,32)","guid":"hqwCtBntAl88pZ12o0H-0g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"0","text":"Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"- Sepsis con hipotensión persistente que requiere vasopresores para mantener PAM ≥65 mmHg","guid":"G30X4wgKaJ9dhudCUUy3Sg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"- Hiperlactatemia >2 mmol/L a pesar de reanimación con volumen adecuado (21)","guid":"h1-iVnzwMA7maAUNvyyKzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"- Mecanismos de falla circulatoria complejos y superpuestos(8)","guid":"oI6AJOudeNP9M8z3UkyU6A","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"- Algunos pacientes permanecen hipovolémicos incluso después de carga inicial de fluidos, sugiriendo beneficio de volumen adicional(9)","guid":"qYL2gdEfa3bDx7Aa3PZyBg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"- Otros con PAD muy baja podrían beneficiarse de aumentar dosis de vasopresores en lugar de más fluidos potencialmente dañinos(10-12)","guid":"RygBLhies7rELni-O-tA-Q","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"- Identificación precoz de disfunción VI/VD podría guiar ajuste hemodinámico para limitar intervenciones deletéreas(13)","guid":"nChtZjL4gUgpCLv3IclHcg","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"9","text":"- Caracterización de estos fenotipos cardiovasculares podría llevar a reanimación más personalizada y mejores resultados(13-15)","guid":"6yPK1RRjwVNsYsHQf9qPvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"- Mortalidad sustancial a pesar de investigación extensa(1,2)","guid":"0jvpaMf9kManvkySMs2mVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"- No hay consenso sobre mejor\\Nestrategia de reanimación inicial(1,2)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"0","text":"- Más de 4h desde\\Ndiagnóstico de shock\\Nséptico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"- Cirugía o hemodiálisis\\Naguda anticipada en período\\Nde intervención de 6h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"- Sangrado activo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"- Estado de no\\Nreanimación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"- Cirrosis Child B-C","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"- Enfermedad subyacente con\\Nexpectativa de vida <90 días","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"- Embarazo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"- SDRA severo\\Nconcomitante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"0","text":"- Pacientes en quienes no se puede\\Nevaluar adecuadamente el TRC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"- Hipotensión persistente que\\Nrequiere vasopresores para\\NPAM ≥65 mmHg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"- Hiperlactatemia\\N>2 mmol/L(21)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"- Signos de hipoperfusión tisular\\N(TRC >3 seg, moteado, ∆pCO2(v-a)\\Nelevada, etc.)(4,32,33)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"0","text":"- Lactato >2 mmol/L OR 4.9 (95% CI: 1.\\N6-14.7) para mortalidad(4)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"- SvcO2 <70% asociado a\\Nmayor mortalidad(4)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"- ∆pCO2(v-a) >6 mmHg\\Npredice hipoperfusión tisular\\Ny mal pronóstico(21)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"0","text":"- Criterios Sepsis-3: hipotensión persistente\\Nque requiere vasopresores para PAM ≥65 mmHg\\N+ lactatemia >2 mmol/L(21)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"- Otras causas de shock distributivo:\\Nanafiláctico, neurogénico, etc.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"0","text":"- Shock cardiogénico,\\Nhipovolémico u obstructivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:(2,4,32,33)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"- Identificación y control del\\Nfoco séptico (prioridad)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"0","text":"- Metas\\Nhemodinámicas\\Niniciales:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"- PAM >65 mmHg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"- FC <120 lpm","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"- SatO2 >94%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"0","text":"- Hb >7-8 g/dL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"0","text":"- Fluidoterapia\\Ncon cristaloides","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"0","text":"- Norepinefrina como\\Nvasopresor de 1ª línea (titular)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"0","text":"- Evaluar respuesta a fluidos y\\Nevitar balance positivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"0","text":"- Puede considerarse:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"0","text":"- Vasopresina 0.03-0.04 U/min\\Nsi NE >0.3 mcg/kg/min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"0","text":"- Dobutamina 2.5-7.5\\Nmcg/kg/min si disfunción VI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"- Ajuste de VM si falla VD (PEEP <10\\NcmH2O, Pplat <28 cmH2O)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"0","text":"- Score SOFA: predice mortalidad,\\Nsirve para seguimiento (19)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"- Criterios AKI-KDIGO:\\Nmonitoreo de función renal (20)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"0","text":"- Medición seriada de\\Nlactato, SvcO2, ∆pCO2(v-a),\\NHb, TRC(1,2,4,32,33)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"0","text":"- Evaluación\\Nmultidisciplinaria\\N(intensivista, infectólogo,\\Nnefrólogo, etc.)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"0","text":"Aspectos Geriátricos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"0","text":"- Mayor mortalidad\\Nen >65 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"0","text":"- Considerar mayor riesgo de\\Nsobrecarga de volumen","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"0","text":"- Polifarmacia aumenta riesgo de\\Ninteracciones farmacológicas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"- Valoración geriátrica integral es\\Nclave para optimizar manejo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"(1) Cecconi M, et al.\\NLancet. 2018;392:75-87.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"0","text":"(2) Evan